title: Leo4All v3 patch 10.5.3 by JaS
description:
This ppf will bring your Leo4all V3 iso up to date with 10.5.3. 

This does use chameleon now for the dvd boot loader so iany users with the Jmicron dvd issue (not found) will not have this problem after applying this ppf. 

Also users that had reboot issues ( sse2 and some sse3) should apply this ppf and try again. New front side bus detection has been added to chameleon to allow booting on these systems. 

Thanks to zef and Kabyl for the additions to Chameleon. 

Thanks to eddie for leo4all. 

Thanks to everyone in the OsX86 community for keeping it going 

Enjoy, 
JaS
